data.description: Great 4 Bedroom Split-Level Home located near walking trail & park/playground features vaulted main living area, spacious walk-out lower level & Lg Deck overlooking tranquil Backyard! Updated Roof, Siding & HVAC system. Home has 2 Bedrooms up, including Primary Bedroom with Walk-Thru Full Bath. Kitchen has hanging pot rack, abundance of cabinetry & stainless-steel appliances, including gas range. Adjacent Dining area has patio door leading out to 19x13 Deck with amazing view! Home has some updated light fixtures but needs some flooring and a little TLC. Great potential!
